dct_title_s: County map of the state of California
dct_description_sm: Insets: San Francisco. Scale [ca. 1:24,400] -- San Francisco Bay and vicinity.
Shows settlements, railroads, rivers, etc.; San Francisco map shows wards, major buildings, aqueduct, etc.
"Entered according to Act of Congress in the year 1880 by S. Augustus Mitchell in the office of the Librarian of Congress at Washington."
From Mitchell, S. Augustus. Mitchell's new general atlas. Philadelphia :S. Augustus Mitchell, 1880.
